ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Consenting to the Amendment to Section 15 of Certain Self-Government Agreements
PrecisOrder consenting to the amendment of section 15 to each of the Champagne and Aishihik First Nations Self-Government Agreement, Teslin Tlingit Council Self-Government Agreement, First Nation of Nacho Nyak Dun Self-Government Agreement, Vuntut Gwitchin First Nation Self-Government Agreement, Little Salmon/Carmacks First Nation Self-Government Agreement, Selkirk First Nation Self-Government Agreement, Tr’ondëk Hwëch’in Self-Government Agreement, Ta’an Kwach’an Council Self-Government Agreement, Kluane First Nation Self-Government Agreement, Kwanlin Dun First Nation Self-Government Agreement and Carcross/Tagish First Nation Self-Government Agreement in order to provide for two tax relief measures.
